			<h3>Who Are We</h3>		
		<p>We are a small digital agency located in the Central New Jersey area with clients around the globe. We work as hard as possible to help small to medium size business with their website needs.</p>		
			<h3>Our Mission</h3>		
		<p>Our mission is to create a strong presence on the internet for the businesses we work with. You should not have to worry about your website generating leads for you, that is our job.</p>		
			<h3>What We Do
</h3>		
