			<h2>Our 6-D Process</h2>		
			<h6>01.</h6>		
			<h4>Discover</h4>		
		<p>Our first step is to discover your market and what works best for you. We want the best outcome for your business so some research needs to be done to achieve that.</p>		
			<h6>02.</h6>		
			<h4>Define</h4>		
		<p>We will then define and refine what we have found. We give you feedback on what we think would work best and what you can do better than your competitors in the same market.</p>		
			<h6>03.</h6>		
			<h4>Design</h4>		
		<p>Creating an awesome design that fits in your niche market is right up our alley. We love coming up with great designs that fits your brand and company perfectly.</p>		
			<h6>04.</h6>		
			<h4>Develop</h4>		
		<p>Once we agree on a design, we then build the whole site out and implement anything that needs to be done. Whether that be an eCommerce store or a simple site generating leads, we are on it.</p>		
			<h6>05.</h6>		
			<h4>Deploy</h4>		
		<p>Once ready, we will handle all the deployment as well. No need for you to research how to get a site off the ground (unless you want to of course) because we can do that all for you.</p>		
			<h6>06.</h6>		
			<h4>Deliver</h4>		
		<p>Delivering our finished product is what we do best. We promise you will love the effort and hard work we put in to your businesses website.</p>		
